<p><cs><col><b>Varying hare</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>any hare
or rabbit which becomes white in winter, especially the common hare of
the Northern United States and Canada.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

